description: Beautifully updated two bedroom condo within walking distance to the T, parks, the beach, and all that Southie has to offer. High-end Modern kitchen with Stainless Steel Appliances, beautiful marble countertops & backsplash. Modern updated bath with subway tile bath. The high ceilings and bright color palette create space in the light filled unit, while gorgeous hardwood floors flow seamlessly throughout. With its own exclusive use of a deeded and private fenced in backyard and patio, you can garden and entertain in style. Unit has in-unit laundry, additional dedicated storage space in the basement, a new water heater and HVAC system, and building has a newer roof and freshly painted exterior.
